---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import CrosswordSolver from '../components/CrosswordSolver.svelte';
---

<MainLayout title="Crossword Solver" description="Free crossword solver tool. Enter any clue with an optional letter pattern to find answers instantly from multiple archives.">
  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="bc-sep">/</span>
        <span>Crossword Solver</span>
      </nav>

      <CrosswordSolver client:load />

      <div class="content-section">
        <h2 class="content-heading">How Our Crossword Solver Works</h2>
        <p class="content-text">
          Our crossword solver checks historical archive matches first, then adds extra non-archive suggestions underneath when they are available. That means the most trustworthy stored crossword hits stay at the top, while broader guesses still help when the archive is thin.
        </p>
        <p class="content-text">
          You can narrow results in two ways: enter a letter pattern with question marks for unknown letters, or tap a letter-count chip to auto-fill the right answer length. This helps a lot on short clues where many possible answers can look similar.
        </p>

        <h2 class="content-heading">Pattern Matching Guide</h2>
        <p class="content-text">
          The pattern field lets you describe the answer shape you are looking for. Use uppercase letters for known positions and question marks (`?`) for unknown letters. For example, if you know the answer is four letters long and looks like `O??O`, enter that pattern directly. If you only know the length, tap the `4` letter chip and the solver will search with `????`.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .page-section { padding: 0 0 48px; }
  .breadcrumb { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-top: 16px; font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .breadcrumb a { color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .bc-sep { color: var(--color-border); }
  .content-section { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding-top: 28px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .content-heading { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .content-text { color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 14px; }
</style>
